  sabayon-2.22.0.ebuild:
  sabayon uses gnome-vfs (provided by gnome-python) to watch files

  29 May 2008; Ali Polatel <hawking@gentoo.org> sabayon-2.22.0.ebuild:
  python_mod_optimize is ROOT aware.

  29 Mar 2008; Gilles Dartiguelongue <eva@gentoo.org> sabayon-2.22.0.ebuild:
  remove pam from DEPEND, it is unneeded since we pass
  --enable-console-helper=no which prevents pam files to be installed,
  bug #147842

